Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph chapter list

chapter list

Purpose:
  List every chapter in the `.sdpub` chapter tree.

Usage:
  wikigraph chapter list <path> [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]

Output shape:
  [<chapterId>] <stage> <title-or-[untitled]>

Behavior:
  - Includes summary-stage and unfinished chapters.
  - Indents child chapters under their parent.
  - The bracketed number is the chapter id used by `chapter` and `queue add --chapter`.
  - Does not call an LLM provider.
  - Does not mutate chapter content or summaries.

Use this before mutation:
  Discover ids with:
    wikigraph chapter list <path>

See also:
  - wikigraph index --help
  - wikigraph chapter status --help
  - wikigraph help command
